<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="goodness-n">goodness <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɡʊdnəs/    美 /'ɡʊdnəs/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>善良；仁慈；上帝：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Thank goodness</strong>!
谢天谢地！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He did it <strong>out of the goodness of his heart</strong>.
他出于好心做了那件事。</p></div></div>